Package com.commercetools.api.models.shopping_list

Class ShoppingListLineItemImpl

java.lang.Object
com.commercetools.api.models.shopping_list.ShoppingListLineItemImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
Customizable<ShoppingListLineItem>, ShoppingListLineItem, ModelBase
public class ShoppingListLineItemImpl extends Object implements ShoppingListLineItem, ModelBase

ShoppingListLineItems are Line Items that contain references to ProductVariants in a Product.

In addition to standard Reference Expansion, a ShoppingListLineItem offers expansion on productSlug and variant, defined with the query parameter expand.
